Placeholder images for SinCity Child Theme:

Required:
- logo.png              (SinCity wordmark, 400x80px, transparent PNG)
- logo-watermark.png    (white logo for player overlay, 200x40px, ~15% opacity white)
- hero-home.jpg         (homepage hero background, 2400x1000px, 21:9)
- city-silhouette.png   (skyline overlay for hero, 2400x800px, semi-transparent PNG)
- cat-normal.jpg        (Normal Porn category card, 800x450px, 16:9)
- cat-hentai.jpg        (Hentai category card, 800x450px, 16:9)
- cat-jav.jpg           (JAV category card, 800x450px, 16:9)

Optional:
